        "title": "SDKWork Video Cut 0.1.1",
        "summary": "Multiplatform unsigned preview release metadata for the hardened intelligent slicing desktop application.",
        "content": "Version 0.1.1 carries forward the unreleased 0.1.0 baseline and adds hardened smart slicing, mandatory offline speech-to-text evidence, transcript-backed recovery, subtitle opt-in behavior, multiplatform release workflow governance, and commercial release blockers for signing, checksums, and SBOM evidence.",
        "highlights": [
          "Smart slicing requires speech-to-text evidence for every generated clip",
          "Recovered native slice artifacts without transcript evidence fail closed",
          "Subtitle rendering remains disabled by default and must be explicitly enabled",
